         MACRO
&NAME    LISIGNAL &WK,&COND=
.*       THIS MACRO GENERATES (POSSIBLY INEFFECTIVE) LANGUAGE-
.*       INDEPENDENT CODE TO "SIGNAL" A "CONDITION".
         GBLC  &LICOND            PL/I CONDITION CODE
&NAME    IHBINNRA &WK             WK AREA ADDR IN R1
         LICOND COND=&COND        TRANSLATE CONDITION NAME
         MVC   0(4,R1),=X'&LICOND.0000'     SORE CONDITION ID
         L     R15,=V(LIESIGN)    SIGNAL ROUTINE ADDRESS
         BALR  R14,R15            GO DO A SIGNAL
         MEND
